# Purpose: stable, testable facts for deterministic ENVIRONMENT_INVENTORY.md authoring.
# - Never put real secret values in this file.
# - For secret variables, use `None`, `Redacted`, or `Secret store only` as the example.
# - Use explicit `Unknown ...` statements and track them under `known_unknowns`.
# - Use `None` or `Not applicable` only when that is confirmed project truth.
#
